gov.nist.secauto.decima.core.assessment

Interface AssessmentExecutorFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicAssessmentExecutorFactory, ConcurrentAssessmentExecutorFactory

    public interface AssessmentExecutorFactory
    An interface for a factory that creates AssessmentExecutor instances. The factory object Decima can construct a number of different types of AssessmentExecutorFactory instances.

    In general, implementations of this class are not required to be thread safe, since generation of an AssessmentExecutor will typically be handled in a single thread.
